                        za stimulaciju mišića. Impulsi tjeraju mišiće da se kontrahiraju i opuštaju. Dakle, oni simuliraju svoje prirodno kretanje,
                        ali donose puno bolje rezultate, kao što su:</p>
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-3">
                            <div class="text-center">
                                <div class="p-4 bg-primary rounded d-flex" style="align-items: center; justify-content: center;">
                                    <img src="~/images/fitness_icons/arm-muscles-icon.svg" style="max-width: 90px; max-height: 90px; width: auto; height: auto; aspect-ratio: 1 /1;" />
                                </div>
                                <div class="my-2">
                                    <h5>Dinamičan Rast</h5>
                                    <h5>Mišića</h5>
                                </div> 
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-3">
                            <div class="text-center">
                                <div class="p-4 bg-primary rounded d-flex" style="align-items: center; justify-content: center;">
                                    <img src="~/images/fitness_icons/women-weight-decrease-icon.svg" style="max-width: 90px; max-height: 90px; width: auto; height: auto; aspect-ratio: 1 /1;" />
                                </div>
                                <div class="my-2">
                                    <h5>Brzo Smanjenje </h5>
                                    <h5>Masnog Tkiva</h5>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-3">
                            <div class="text-center">
                                <div class="p-4 bg-primary rounded d-flex" style="align-items: center; justify-content: center;">
                                    <img src="~/images/fitness_icons/man-back-pain-icon.svg" style="max-width: 90px; max-height: 90px; width: auto; height: auto; aspect-ratio: 1 /1;"  />
                                </div>
                                <div class="my-2">
                                    <h5>Bolje</h5>
                                    <h5>Držanje</h5>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-3">
                            <div class="text-center">
                                <div class="p-4 bg-primary rounded d-flex" style="align-items: center; justify-content: center;">
                                    <img src="~/images/fitness_icons/neuron-icon.svg" style="max-width: 90px; max-height: 90px; width: auto; height: auto; aspect-ratio: 1 /1;" />
                                </div>
                                <div class="my-2">
                                    <h5>Više Živčanih </h5>
                                    <h5>Veza</h5>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    @*<button type="button" class="btn btn-primary border-0 rounded-pill px-4 py-3 mt-5">Više o programu</button>*@
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<!-- About End -->

